The nursery school is a part, too, offices have understood the architects.
The administration building Avriopoint of Brno is the new headquarters of society Arch. design.
No one could have expected that it is also home to a nursery school with all that is needed - walls of colors, furniture, imaginative toys and finally a playground miniature on the terrace.
Since October last year, had access to the children of employees of Arch. design.
The company projets-architectonique Arch. design. whose workshops have produced a large number of buildings in Brno, thought his mini nursery school of business since the start of the building Avriopoint.
It employs about 90 people, most of the age to have children and it is important that women architects and project leaders to quickly return to work.
At the same time that time decreased, nursery school is a proposed bonuses to its employees by society Arch. design. as part of its social agenda.
The builders and architects have the opportunity to combine work taking care for children.
Employees of Arch.Design.eux-mêmes who have imagined this nursery school and with the support of the direction they were able to obtain a contribution of the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mini nursery school is funded by the European Social Fund through the operational programme of human resources and budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to the endowments of funding (up to 2,8 mil.de CZK). they were able to buy equipment and appliances and after two years to ensure a qualified staff as well as the establishment.
After the use of the allocation of funding (two years) society Arch. design. has the obligation after 3 years of the mini nursery school on its own funds.
The project lasted a year and it is society Economy rating that has helped to make the request.
The child care is provided by a qualified staff, all day a nurse and a teacher of maternal care for children. a child can go to school without maternal age limit but they have more than three anspour most.
As it is a "mini nursery school" there are only 5 children at the same time, but during the day there are more that supersede.
The operation of the school is flexible according to the needs of parents and children of all employees have the same right to use the school without regard to the position of authority.
Although it is agise of care and education, the individual program of the mini nursery school is comparable to that for pre-school education.
Children are not only play but a quality education is also assured - from start to school teaches English.
The class is equipped not only of toys and games imaginative but also a computer that children can use.
The presence of small children in society creates an environment friendly and positive.
Parents can at any time to monitor their child and not having the stress of a delay for the children to a school far from the workplace of parents.
Parents use their time in the most productive.
It is not surprising that creates a natural relationship of loyalty between the employee and the employer.
Arch.design.s' is thus enshrined among the companies that offer a bonus of choice for the recruitment of new employees and who are friendly to the family and through this program makes HR.
