He did not like, for example, the local council as the pillars of the construction empiettent dead on the public.
There was never change, but, on the contrary, only 15 days after the appeal of the city Battlo Josep asked (satisfaction) and got permission to rent the top two floors.
The owner moved upstairs.
In the gallery on the second floor there was a common and a third chamber and a private party of the apartment.
The ground floor was leased to a jewellery.
The full house of six floors is shared by a staircase by which access to a terrace of toît independent.
All the rights and straight lines were cancelled by the basic elements of the reconstruction and their replacement by walls curves.
