The party will be completely connected by opening the doors of rooms and the high society can communicate comfortably or be limited space for private talks more intimate.
The house with the reconstruction of proper talk has also received new facades a toîture non-traditional and two floors and more.
The game to talk with the light is also impressive, glass tiles, blue and white with which is decorated the courtyard and with the wells of lights.
The stake in two colours gives a maximum of light in all the floors of the house.
