How to choose a mattress and a sommier: women have other criteria than men.
Not ostentatious, but rather the quality of the surface on the bed, so the mattress and the sommier give a real basis for a good read.
Of course, they need to complement each other harmoniously to please an user concrete.
The choice for several things are crucial:, weight, height, age, health status and gender of owner.
The type of procedure which will put the mattress and the sommier is also important.
A typical example?
For example, in the country house where the sleeps not continuously mattresses in gum are not appropriate because they are "hot" slowly.
They also have a weight above the mattress in polyurethane standards.
It is necessary to return frequently.
If they do not have enough also channels of breakdown in and if they remain, in addition, on a drawing solid, they retain moisture. the mould can also form.
The habit is also crucial in the choice.
Someone who's clear time abroad where it uses frequently mattresses very thick with a layer rammollissante, will feel hard on a surface low and hard.
"this is how all hokeyistes returning from NHL complain that they cannot sleep there."
"for their shoulders, tired feet and the coast, they needed a layer of foam mattresses with rammollisante lazy."
"such mattresses are also recommended for people with diabetes who have a disorder of the nervous system which therefore assume evil" information "of joints and skin," Sylva Adamczikova who specializes in furniture padding.
That is why a few years ago the mattresses with foam lazy has conquered the hokeyistes and other clients.
"today everything goes well, Tempur, the Italian Magnifex but also the Czech Tropico have mattresses appropriate.
You do not need to be a guy of NHL to see a foam lazy.
This "miracle" works.
She optimisation its rigidity and his form in the heat absorbed or adapts to the warmth of your body.
There is no pressure on you and you do not go back into the night as after a difficult match.
You sleep simply better.
The foam lazy also functions as a protection against the esquarres.
For the choice of mattresses depending on your size, add the length of the feet, or about 21 / 34 cm.
A man and a woman to a size of 180 cm a bed of 210 / 220 cm.
The minimum width for each to a bed in two places should be 90 cm to 180 cm.
For beds in one place, the singles, for example, it is recommended to take at least 120 / 140 cm.
It is convenient in the event of a visit.
However, it is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on their backs you should be hands comfortably with shoulder slightly folded. Prokopova Helena, President of the Association of Bourreliers-matelassiers and decorators who go for several years to the issue of a healthy sleep and ergonomics non-furniture taught in the schools.
For one to two seats each needs its own sommier and mattresses, however, attention during the achât to choose the height of the mattress.
Otherwise you will have to turn the sommier at different heights and is not achievable in all environments.
The foam mattresses should have a minimum height of 14 cm, the mattress springs to at least 15 cm, of this matter to the form and aeration at least three centimeters.
"the infructueuses or in a sitting position on the mattress you should not feel the springs," warns Héléna Prokopova.
Each mattress request a specific type of sommier.
The lit-sommier, when the mattress and the sommier joined together as sisters siamoises, has no place in the bedrooms.
The mattress is aèrent very badly; it must not wash, which is commonly auhourd' today.
And since during the night we normally exudes from 0,2 to 0,75 the sweat it is clear that after 5 / 7 years, the mattresses begins to recall a great (and) clogged sieve.
For this specialists refuse to make the calls on a life of 25 years for a mattress or guaranteed for life.
But to his but.
And a board of experience on the part of sellers: for a mattress of 120 / 140 cm, dispensing, for the surface of the mattress, hygiene or the brainwashing but add rather a buffer of protection that vouspouvez easily withdraw and wash.
And although it is common for surfaces with closure to glissière for the whole thing, that is to say that after the opening has two parts (for the brainwashing and the size of a washing machine that is very important!) or the manipulation for large models (and for a single person) becomes when they cut a fight between a light weight and a lorry on a ring.
You have in your bed a drawing rigid instead of a sommier?
Never!
The maximum for a bed visitors for one night.
However équipez done (if not) of aeration holes and use the mattress to life with a minimum height of 15 cm with springs in sachets (Germany Taschenfederken) and a layer of aeration.
A mattress in polyurethane should not be part of a bed of this type.
For the mattress to slats to unique position with 14 / 18 slats, the mattresses in gum or so-called sandwiches (perhaps a combination of gum and coconut), are the ideal but it will always be better for you to have a mattress with more slats, 28 and above, where the slats are double in the bottom of the kidneys and that it is possible to regulate the rigidity.
For the mattress in several positions should not be mattress springs to because it does not meet the changes of position.
In addition to the regulation of the rigidity of slats can also install a so-called cradle.
It is a special liaison slats which forces even tipping the lamelle to the shoulder of the dormeur "fits well."
For men who have "the broadest shoulders," it is really important.
This thing is already envisaged by the manufacturers of mattresses that for "male" began using a zone rammollissante at the level of the shoulders.
But they also believe women - they provide a surface more soft at the level of the hips.
E-Customer the more difficult it is to frame the wings or platelets with what is called a suspension multiforce.
The pressure contaminate in more points and diinue tension.
But of course, attention, as soon as you use a bad pillow (big and bulky air) on good mattresses and sommier, the "more" disappears.
The basic rule is a pillow simple: the pillow must support the head and gasp must reach only the shoulders, so that the muscles of shoulders could rest.
The recommended size is 50 cm X60 that Scandinavians by exmple prefer.
When one is lying on the side, the pillow must upgrade (with the cradle to the sommier or the area in the rammollie mattresses) match the shoulders.
The modern mattresses still have something in common with the first made from straw and herbs.
The manufacturers still use natural substances or mixtures.
The trend is also organic mattresses.
The raw materials pétrôle, from which it produces the polyurethane, are replaced by natural oils such as soybean oil.
Almost all manufacturers use known precisely soybeans.
"the colour for the mattress means that the heart is manufactured using natural products," said Petr vasicek society Tropico Plus.
The natural substances are used for coating mattresses; one of the first was the aloe vera.
But you can add micro-capsules who develop perfumes forest or lavande.
There are differences between men and women.
While the excerpt of birch to the surface of the mattress absorbs heat and cooling the body, "cooling," and "light" women.
The excerpt from poivre red accelerates the bloodstream and is therefore warmer for the weaker sex.
The current favourite?
The mattress made from foam Cold (she has more oozed with a cellular structure and therefore more respirante than the standard polyurethane and has more elasticity.
The combination of different rigidities of cold gives foam mattresses polyzones who know exactly where the head, the lower back and feet.
You will pay a mattress quality from 7000 Nkr235 and more.
Those who are characterised by their parameters for health have less VAT and are used as instruments for health.
In the Czech Republic, it is Gumotex who has reached the first place.
