The US military has sent Afghnistan a new weapon "intelligent," known only as the XM- 25.
The generals think that this new automatic rifle will have an influence on the conflict with the Taliban and "will change the game" to their benefit.
The new weapon is like a super precise
The projectiles are guided by laser with a precision of a few metres.
The ammunition special 25 mm developed for the gun and containing a highly explosive breaking, functioned as small grenades.
You can AJB00 ammunition in such a way as to explode on contact with the target but also at any point of their ballistic trajectory.
We can therefore use against an enemy that hides behind a barrier, a wall or a gap.
It is also not protected from above and when it is upon a rain of shards of steel, it can be to disable also.
According to Richard Audette who took part in the development of XM- 25, the new gun is the first weapon infantry which uses technology "intelligent."
"the soldier is used mainly in such a way that it is the target, it sends a laser that determines the distance, is a specific target, it corrects its target site and supports the trigger.
"let's say that you have referred to 543 metres."
"when you squeeze the trigger, the gun handles and draws to a distance of 543 metres or less 1, 2, 3 meters," said Audette.
