Christine Lagarde has stressed yesterday at a press conference in Paris: "The Europeans, I believe that it has demonstrated yet again Sunday in the day and night, are obviously solidarity, determined to defend their currencies and monetary zone."
Although relative detente recorded yesterday on the rate of government bonds has played right into the hands of the governments and the ECB.
